# Game Cards Project  

A responsive web project that showcases game information cards with animations and hover effects.  
This project was developed as part of the challenge [NFT Preview Card Component](https://www.frontendmentor.io/challenges/nft-preview-card-component-SbdUL_w0U) from Frontend Mentor, but adapted to a gaming theme.  

---

## Features  

- Responsive Design (Mobile & Desktop)  
- CardList Component with multiple game cards  
- Images generated with Leonardo.ai  
- Custom logo designed with Leonardo.ai  
- Hover effects on cards  
- Animations with [Animate.css](https://animate.style/)  
- Header with navigation bar and logo  
- Organized project structure with branches and commits in English  
- Hosted on GitHub Pages  

---

## Technologies  

- HTML5  
- TailwindCSS (for styling and responsiveness)  
- Animate.css (for animations)  
- Leonardo.ai (for image and logo generation)  
- Git & GitHub (version control and hosting)  

